{"tid":1469904,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(清醒D) 停止所有post割定唔割，同路人係唔會割所以無討論空間","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:45:42.000Z","uid":187404,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6c81b138b83f311007da10c9225fbd4fdf886bd9","tid":1469904,"uid":187404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:32:43.000Z","msg":"現在大家要諗下一步點做，尤其是818全港大遊行<br />\n<br />\n和理非同勇武要互相支持，大家都要有勇有謀<br />\n<br />\n只有團結就無堅不摧，兵來將擋水來土淹<br />\n<br />\n大家係唔同角色要深思熟慮前瞻後顧<br />\n<br />\n不要再討論割與不割<br />\n<br />\n因為同路人大家目標一致係一定唔會割<br />\n<br />\n只會討論下策略或細節將件事越做越好<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><em>赢就一齊贏 輸就正苦輸</em></em></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"9c1ce1210e44f6eedc61b4c56f843f51504b346c","tid":1469904,"uid":187404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c31682cd74381d5c99caa5864deb3fcf5f4634d","tid":1469904,"uid":187404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:33:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81497a657e21c98b97a77f5b46c5c3611f50c6c","tid":1469904,"uid":187404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f